    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a concours-level E92 M3, a definitive example of high-revving, naturally aspirated precision. At its heart is the S65 4.0L V8, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that pulls cleanly to an 8,400 RPM redline. Power is managed through a tactile six-speed manual gearbox and a GKN-sourced M-variable limited-slip differential. The chassis integrity is absolute, featuring the weight-saving carbon fiber roof and Electronic Damper Control (EDC) for optimized suspension kinematics. This specimen has undergone meticulous preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator upgrades, ensuring the internal tolerances and valvetrain remain within factory specifications. Every bushing, link, and subframe mounting point is in pristine condition, offering the communicative steering and lateral stability expected of a flagship M-car.",
      "price": 48500.0,
